0.1.name: wordpress/latest-mobileme-photos
0.1.description:
The plugin checks your MobileMe Webgallery feed and displays thumbnails of photos that have recently been uploaded or changed. The thumbnails link to the fullsize versions in the webgallery. Only public photos are displayed (those accessible via feed).

New in this Version: Fixed feed loading problems
